title: Organic Soy Nail Polish Remover By Karma Organics - Lavender
description:
Finally!  A nail polish remover that really works, without all of the harmful chemicals and harsh odors!  Moisturizing and works quickly to remove nail polish.

Karma Organic's Nail Polish remover is made from an organic soy mixture, and is:

-Free of any petroleum Ingredients
-Packaged in 100% recyclable glass bottles
-Comes in Lavender, Tea Tree, or Unscented with Vitamin E Oil
* 4 Fluid Ounces

Ingredients:
Propylene Carbonate - odorless, colorless liquid used as a solvent
Soybean oil methyl exter - used as a solvent in liquid separations
Tocopheryl acetate (Unscented only) - also known as Vitamin E, common vitamin supplement
